# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:12
translate french jamie1_777c0e1d:

    # "I see Jamie leaving her house and walking out towards her car. I wave at her."
    "Je vois Jamie sortir de chez elle et se diriger vers sa voiture. Je lui fais signe."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:15
translate french jamie1_2848acf3:

    # gnd "Hey there."
    gnd "Salut."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:17
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_008.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_008.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:18
translate french jamie1_d7b2148b:

    # gnd "I'm going out for a coffee before class. Want to join me?"
    gnd "Je vais prendre un café avant les cours. Tu veux venir avec moi ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:19
translate french jamie1_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Bien sûr."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:20
translate french jamie1_d60e5294:

    # gnd "Do you know where Java Lava is?"
    gnd "Tu sais où se trouve Java Lava ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:21
translate french jamie1_6ff82333:

    # pc "Yep."
    pc "Oui."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:23
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice "voices/jamie_006.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_006.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:24
translate french jamie1_55e7809c:

    # gnd "Cool, meet me there."
    gnd "Super, on se retrouve là-bas."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:26
translate french jamie1_2d0bcd97:

    # "She smiles and gets into her car before pulling out and heading down the road."
    "Elle sourit et monte dans sa voiture avant de démarrer et de s'engager sur la route."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:29
translate french jamie1_1da96612:

    # "I get into my car and quickly follow her."
    "Je monte dans ma voiture et la suis rapidement."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:30
translate french jamie1_50a2f2a6:

    # "I wonder why she didn't just want to ride together. It's a little weird since we're coming from pretty much the same place."
    "Je me demande pourquoi elle n’a pas simplement voulu qu’on fasse le trajet ensemble. C’est un peu bizarre vu qu’on vient pratiquement du même endroit."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:32
translate french jamie1_f376757c:

    # "I pull into the Java Lava parking lot and can smell the scent of the coffee drifting out of the entire building."
    "Je me gare sur le parking de Java Lava et je sens l’odeur du café qui s’échappe de tout le bâtiment."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:33
translate french jamie1_01e0166e:

    # "I park next to Jamie, who is still sitting in her car."
    "Je me gare à côté de Jamie, qui est toujours assise dans sa voiture."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:34
translate french jamie1_15a1f80d:

    # "She steps out at the same time that I do."
    "Elle sort en même temps que moi."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:38
translate french jamie1_32e82c5b:

    # gnd "Hey there, fancy meeting you here."
    gnd "Salut, quelle coïncidence de te voir ici."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:39
translate french jamie1_c2309d17:

    # pc "It is quite a coincidence. Shall we drink together?"
    pc "C'est une sacrée coïncidence. On va prendre un café ensemble ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:40
translate french jamie1_bb6e9df1:

    # gnd "Yes, I think we should."
    gnd "Oui, je pense qu'on devrait."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:41
translate french jamie1_bec125c3:

    # "We walk up to the front door together. I hold the door open and the barista greets us as we walk in."
    "On se dirige ensemble vers la porte d'entrée. Je tiens la porte ouverte et la barista nous accueille quand on entre."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:45
translate french jamie1_f6e4b44a:

    # "She looks familiar, but I can't place her. Probably just somebody I've seen around town. It's not a very big place."
    "Elle me dit quelque chose, mais je n'arrive pas à la situer. C'est sûrement juste quelqu'un que j'ai croisé en ville. Ce n'est pas un endroit très grand."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:47
translate french jamie1_f1d232e2:

    # "Tammy is working again today. I guess she works a lot."
    "Tammy travaille encore aujourd'hui. Je suppose qu'elle travaille beaucoup."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:48
translate french jamie1_e532df5e:

    # "Jamie and I place our orders, and the barista makes them without much small talk."
    "Jamie et moi passons notre commande, et la barista nous sert sans faire de bavardages."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:49
translate french jamie1_4b7ec1d8:

    # "Then we take our drinks and sit across from each other at a small table in the dining area."
    "Puis nous prenons nos boissons et nous asseyons face à face à une petite table dans la salle."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:52
translate french jamie1_7ca9f991:

    # "Jamie seems unusually shy. We'd never had a problem talking to each other when we were younger, but things are different now."
    "Jamie semble inhabituellement timide. Nous n’avions jamais eu de mal à nous parler quand nous étions plus jeunes, mais les choses sont différentes maintenant."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:53
translate french jamie1_e60beee6:

    # "She simply looks at me, and when I look back, she averts her eyes and smiles."
    "Elle se contente de me regarder, et quand je la regarde à mon tour, elle détourne les yeux et sourit."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:54
translate french jamie1_4d348656:

    # "I don't know what to talk about really."
    "Je ne sais pas vraiment de quoi parler."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:55
translate french jamie1_3fd979ca:

    # pc "So, you're going to school this semester?"
    pc "Alors, tu vas à l'université ce semestre ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:56
translate french jamie1_cefd0447:

    # "It seems like an easy question to get us started talking about something."
    "Ça me semble être une question facile pour lancer la conversation."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:58
translate french jamie1_e7bf7de1:

    # gnd "Yeah, Skyhill."
    gnd "Oui, à Skyhill."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:59
translate french jamie1_076d61a1:

    # pc "What's your major?"
    pc "Tu fais quoi comme études ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:60
translate french jamie1_a9ffb9a9:

    # gnd "I'm in the teaching program. I'll be starting my in-class assistant position this semester, where I help a teacher for two periods a day."
    gnd "Je suis en formation pour devenir enseignante. Je commence ce semestre comme assistante en classe, où j'aide un prof pendant deux cours par jour."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:61
translate french jamie1_53927809:

    # pc "Oh, that's exciting."
    pc "Oh, c'est génial."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:62
translate french jamie1_d7ae6789:

    # gnd "Yeah, I'm pretty nervous about it actually."
    gnd "Oui, en fait, ça me rend assez nerveuse."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:63
translate french jamie1_5924379f:

    # pc "You shouldn't be. You'll do great, I'm sure."
    pc "Tu ne devrais pas. Tu t'en sortiras très bien, j'en suis sûre."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:64
translate french jamie1_30b2342d:

    # pc "It doesn't surprise me that you're going to become a teacher."
    pc "Ça ne me surprend pas que tu deviennes enseignante."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:65
translate french jamie1_d096758b:

    # pc "You always used to help me with my schoolwork. I don't think I would have passed 8th grade English without your help."
    pc "Tu m'aidais toujours avec mes devoirs. Je ne pense pas que j'aurais réussi mon anglais de 4e sans ton aide."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:67
translate french jamie1_8ab7f6ac:

    # gnd "Oh you definitely wouldn't have. Your essays were horrible."
    gnd "Oh, c'est certain que non. Tes dissertations étaient horribles."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:68
translate french jamie1_ba5dd62d:

    # pc "They didn't get much better in high school either, or college."
    pc "Ils ne se sont pas beaucoup améliorés au lycée non plus, ni à la fac."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:70
translate french jamie1_4bc7c623:

    # gnd "So what are you majoring in?"
    gnd "Alors, tu fais quoi comme études ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:71
translate french jamie1_8dfe1fc1:

    # pc "Quantum Science, but I'm having to take all my basics this year, since I didn't take them before."
    pc "La science quantique, mais je dois suivre tous les cours de base cette année, vu que je ne les ai pas faits avant."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:72
translate french jamie1_e89ebb70:

    # gnd "Oh cool. Quantum Science, like your dad huh?"
    gnd "Oh cool. La science quantique, comme ton père, hein ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:73
translate french jamie1_73fe1c32:

    # pc "Yeah. Different types, but similar."
    pc "Ouais. Des domaines différents, mais similaires."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:74
translate french jamie1_d6a36df7:

    # gnd "I wouldn't have expected that from you."
    gnd "Je ne m’attendais pas à ça de ta part."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:75
translate french jamie1_d98cce84:

    # pc "Why's that?"
    pc "Pourquoi ça ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:76
translate french jamie1_6e902e84:

    # gnd "Well, you never seemed like the type to enjoy the science and math stuff. I always thought that you'd end up being a used car salesman or something."
    gnd "Eh bien, tu n’as jamais eu l’air d’être du genre à aimer les sciences et les maths. J’ai toujours pensé que tu finirais par devenir vendeur de voitures d’occasion ou quelque chose comme ça."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:77
translate french jamie1_c0131acd:

    # pc "Wow! Harsh!"
    pc "Ouah ! C’est dur !"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:80
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice "voices/jamie_009.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_009.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:81
translate french jamie1_775544cc:

    # gnd "I'm sorry! I didn't mean anything bad by it, I just meant that you were always very charismatic and fast-talking, but never interested in studies."
    gnd "Je suis désolée ! Je ne voulais pas dire de mal, je voulais juste dire que tu as toujours été très charismatique et que tu parlais vite, mais que tu ne t’intéressais jamais aux études."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:82
translate french jamie1_3b20ba0b:

    # gnd "I should have said lawyer - that would have been nicer, I guess. Not that there's anything wrong with used car salesmen though."
    gnd "J'aurais dû dire avocat – ça aurait été plus sympa, je suppose. Non pas qu'il y ait quoi que ce soit de mal à être vendeur de voitures d'occasion."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:83
translate french jamie1_d28b9880:

    # pc "Well I'm a lot different than I was when I was 13."
    pc "Eh bien, je suis très différent de ce que j'étais à 13 ans."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:86
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_3:

    # voice "voices/jamie_054.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_054.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:87
translate french jamie1_59601283:

    # gnd "Speaking of when we were 13, there was something I wanted to ask you."
    gnd "En parlant de quand on avait 13 ans, il y a quelque chose que je voulais te demander."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:88
translate french jamie1_88fa21e7:

    # pc "Ask away."
    pc "Vas-y, demande."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:90
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_4:

    # voice "voices/jamie_055.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_055.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:92
translate french jamie1_7520d05b:

    # gnd "Why did you break up with me?"
    gnd "Pourquoi tu as rompu avec moi ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:93
translate french jamie1_7eba9d8e:

    # "My stomach does a sort of backflip. This is not what I had been expecting at all."
    "J’ai l’estomac qui fait une sorte de saut périlleux. Je ne m’attendais pas du tout à ça."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:94
translate french jamie1_b464fd63:

    # pc "Break up with you? What do you mean?"
    pc "Rompre avec toi ? Qu’est-ce que tu veux dire ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:97
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_5:

    # voice "voices/jamie_056.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_056.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:98
translate french jamie1_208f93af:

    # gnd "In middle school. We had been neighbors and friends for pretty much our whole lives."
    gnd "Au collège. On était voisins et amis depuis pratiquement toujours."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:100
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_6:

    # voice "voices/jamie_057.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_057.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:101
translate french jamie1_03b1922c:

    # gnd "We'd play at each other's houses. You were my first kiss. You were the first boy to touch my boobs, although there wasn't much there at the time."
    gnd "On jouait chez l’un ou chez l’autre. Tu as été mon premier baiser. Tu as été le premier garçon à me toucher les seins, même s’il n’y avait pas grand-chose à l’époque."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:104
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_7:

    # voice "voices/jamie_058.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_058.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:105
translate french jamie1_d37ad228:

    # gnd "We went to Homecoming together. Remember?"
    gnd "On est allés au bal de fin d’année ensemble. Tu te souviens ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:108
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_8:

    # voice "voices/jamie_059.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_059.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:109
translate french jamie1_a5fe0c77:

    # gnd "Then, out of nowhere, you just stopped talking to me."
    gnd "Et puis, d’un coup, tu as arrêté de me parler."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:111
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_060.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_060.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:112
translate french jamie1_a94569ad:

    # gnd "You didn't come over and see me anymore, you didn't answer my phone calls, you didn't even acknowledge me in the halls at school."
    gnd "Tu ne venais plus me voir, tu ne répondais plus à mes appels, tu ne me saluais même plus dans les couloirs de l’école."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:113
translate french jamie1_60a987f0:

    # pc "Wait, what? I don't remember doing any of that."
    pc "Attends, quoi ? Je ne me souviens pas avoir fait tout ça."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:114
translate french jamie1_7d86fb5a:

    # pc "We just stopped hanging out together. You had different friends and so did I."
    pc "On a juste arrêté de traîner ensemble. Tu avais d’autres amis, et moi aussi."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:116
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_10:

    # voice "voices/jamie_061.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_061.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:117
translate french jamie1_dc86cca2:

    # gnd "Is that what you think happened?"
    gnd "C’est ce que tu penses qu’il s’est passé ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:118
translate french jamie1_69b6e4a8:

    # pc "From what I remember. That was a long time ago."
    pc "D'après ce dont je me souviens. C'était il y a longtemps."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:120
translate french jamie1_58fea4ec:

    # "She sighs and looks away from me, her bottom lip sticking out. My response obviously made her upset, but I truly don't remember things happening that way."
    "Elle soupire et détourne le regard, la lèvre inférieure en avant. Ma réponse l'a manifestement bouleversée, mais je ne me souviens vraiment pas que les choses se soient passées ainsi."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:121
translate french jamie1_a62cc161:

    # "I did stop going over to her house, but that was just because we stopped hanging out as much."
    "J'ai arrêté d'aller chez elle, mais c'était simplement parce qu'on ne traînait plus autant ensemble."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:122
translate french jamie1_3ad28c2d:

    # "I might have ignored some of her phone calls, but I don't think it was intentional. I was just doing other things and it slipped my mind."
    "J'ai peut-être ignoré certains de ses appels, mais je ne pense pas que c'était intentionnel. J’étais simplement occupé à autre chose et ça m’est sorti de l’esprit."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:123
translate french jamie1_7e6fa894:

    # "And I didn't greet everybody I knew in the halls every time we passed - that's just silly."
    "Et je ne saluais pas toutes les personnes que je connaissais dans les couloirs à chaque fois qu’on se croisait – c’est tout simplement ridicule."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:124
translate french jamie1_515956f7:

    # "But there is something else. I do remember being upset at her about something. Maybe I did consciously ignore her?"
    "Mais il y a autre chose. Je me souviens bien d’avoir été fâché contre elle à propos de quelque chose. Peut-être que je l’ai ignorée consciemment ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:127
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_11:

    # voice "voices/jamie_062.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_062.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:128
translate french jamie1_dce96005:

    # gnd "It wasn't just the normal growing apart. Something happened, and you just cut me off completely."
    gnd "Ce n’était pas juste une simple distance qui s’était installée entre nous. Il s’est passé quelque chose, et tu m’as complètement coupé la parole."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:130
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_12:

    # voice "voices/jamie_063.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_063.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:131
translate french jamie1_98593801:

    # gnd "Every time I tried to ask you why, you blew me off, until eventually I just got the hint that you didn't like me anymore."
    gnd "Chaque fois que j’essayais de te demander pourquoi, tu m’esoyais, jusqu’à ce que je finisse par comprendre que tu ne m’aimais plus."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:132
translate french jamie1_306adf54:

    # pc "I didn't stop liking--"
    pc "Je n’ai pas cessé de t’aimer..."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:134
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_13:

    # voice "voices/jamie_064.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_064.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:135
translate french jamie1_02d938ef:

    # gnd "It was right after that Homecoming dance. We had a good time there. I know we did."
    gnd "C’était juste après ce bal de fin d’année. On s’était bien amusés là-bas. Je sais qu’on s’était bien amusés."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:137
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_14:

    # voice "voices/jamie_065.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_065.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:138
translate french jamie1_b0be8140:

    # gnd "We danced like middle school kids, just holding each other and swaying back and forth."
    gnd "On a dansé comme des collégiens, juste en se tenant l’un contre l’autre et en se balançant d’avant en arrière."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:140
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_15:

    # voice "voices/jamie_066.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_066.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:141
translate french jamie1_7107383b:

    # gnd "Then we snuck off to the corner and made out for the rest of the night."
    gnd "Puis on s’est éclipsés dans un coin et on s’est embrassés pendant le reste de la soirée."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:143
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_16:

    # voice "voices/jamie_067.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_067.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:144
translate french jamie1_6e0d44b1:

    # gnd "Afterwards, I thought I did something wrong. That you didn't like kissing me or something. That I had made you mad."
    gnd "Après, j’ai cru que j’avais fait quelque chose de mal. Que tu n’aimais pas m’embrasser ou quelque chose comme ça. Que je t’avais mise en colère."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:146
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_17:

    # voice "voices/jamie_068.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_068.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:147
translate french jamie1_ae5a2abe:

    # gnd "So what was it? What happened?"
    gnd "Alors, c’était quoi ? Qu’est-ce qui s’est passé ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:148
translate french jamie1_820e82ce:

    # pc "Homecoming? That was 8th grade?"
    pc "Le bal de fin d’année ? C’était en quatrième ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:149
translate french jamie1_5c9ff614:

    # "She nods."
    "Elle hoche la tête."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:150
translate french jamie1_dab6ae1d:

    # pc "Ugh. I remember now."
    pc "Ah. Je m’en souviens maintenant."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:152
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_18:

    # voice "voices/jamie_069.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_069.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:153
translate french jamie1_27030523:

    # gnd "Oh really?"
    gnd "Ah bon ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:154
translate french jamie1_791da015:

    # pc "Do you remember my friend Tosh?"
    pc "Tu te souviens de mon ami Tosh ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:156
translate french jamie1_3b8202ee:

    # "She nods again."
    "Elle hoche à nouveau la tête."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:157
translate french jamie1_35a1b275:

    # pc "Well we were best friends at the time. We rode bikes everywhere and played video games together."
    pc "Eh bien, on était meilleurs amis à l’époque. On allait partout à vélo et on jouait aux jeux vidéo ensemble."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:159
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_19:

    # voice "voices/jamie_070.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_070.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:160
translate french jamie1_5dcba36c:

    # gnd "I remember. You kind of stopped hanging out with me as much once he started coming around."
    gnd "Je m’en souviens. Tu as en quelque sorte arrêté de traîner autant avec moi quand il a commencé à fréquenter la maison."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:161
translate french jamie1_d2697e62:

    # pc "Yeah, well after the Homecoming dance, he told me that he heard you saying stuff in the Spanish class that you shared with him."
    pc "Ouais, eh bien après le bal de fin d’année, il m’a dit qu’il t’avait entendue dire des trucs en cours d’espagnol, que tu suivais avec lui."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:162
translate french jamie1_09200a36:

    # pc "Stuff like that you didn't really like me and that you only went to the dance with me because I gave you chocolates and flowers and stuff."
    pc "Des trucs du genre que tu ne m’aimais pas vraiment et que tu n’étais allée au bal avec moi que parce que je t’avais offert des chocolats, des fleurs et tout ça."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:165
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_20:

    # voice "voices/jamie_071.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_071.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:166
translate french jamie1_9a75f2cb:

    # gnd "That's ridiculous! I never said anything like that!"
    gnd "C'est ridicule ! Je n'ai jamais dit ça !"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:167
translate french jamie1_358eaba7:

    # pc "I believe you!"
    pc "Je te crois !"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:168
translate french jamie1_9638be50:

    # pc "But at the time, I thought that Tosh was completely honest, and I trusted everything he said."
    pc "Mais à l'époque, je pensais que Tosh était tout à fait honnête, et je croyais tout ce qu'il disait."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:169
translate french jamie1_89d02a73:

    # pc "It wasn't until high school that I realized that he was completely full of shit."
    pc "Ce n'est qu'au lycée que j'ai réalisé qu'il racontait n'importe quoi."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:170
translate french jamie1_b50f91a5:

    # pc "I think he's in jail now."
    pc "Je crois qu'il est en prison maintenant."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:173
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_21:

    # voice "voices/jamie_072.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_072.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:174
translate french jamie1_11f27db5:

    # gnd "So that's it? We were friends our whole lives, but you trusted some new guy friend from school and didn't even talk to me about it? Didn't even let me defend myself?"
    gnd "C'est tout ? On a été amis toute notre vie, mais tu as fait confiance à un nouveau copain de l'école et tu ne m'en as même pas parlé ? Tu ne m'as même pas laissé me défendre ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:178
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_22:

    # voice "voices/jamie_073.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_073.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:179
translate french jamie1_4975276b:

    # gnd "Hell yes, you were."
    gnd "Bien sûr que oui."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:182
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_23:

    # voice "voices/jamie_074.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_074.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:183
translate french jamie1_4e3ae829:

    # gnd "What does it matter?"
    gnd "Qu'est-ce que ça change ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:185
translate french jamie1_9872e61d:

    # "She looks at me, tears pooling in her eyes."
    "Elle me regarde, les larmes aux yeux."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:187
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_24:

    # voice "voices/jamie_075.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_075.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:188
translate french jamie1_1692a6fc:

    # gnd "You broke my heart. I know it's all middle school stuff, but you'd be surprised how much things that happen during that time in your life affect your mindset."
    gnd "Tu m'as brisé le cœur. Je sais que ce ne sont que des histoires de collège, mais tu serais surpris de voir à quel point les événements de cette période de ta vie influencent ton état d'esprit."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:190
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_25:

    # voice "voices/jamie_076.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_076.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:191
translate french jamie1_76ad11a6:

    # gnd "I was so in love with you, you wouldn't believe it."
    gnd "J’étais tellement amoureuse de toi, tu ne le croirais pas."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:193
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_26:

    # voice "voices/jamie_077.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_077.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:194
translate french jamie1_e649708c:

    # gnd "You cutting me off like that sort of flipped a switch in my brain."
    gnd "Le fait que tu m’aies rejetée comme ça, ça a en quelque sorte déclenché un déclic dans mon cerveau."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:196
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_27:

    # voice "voices/jamie_078.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_078.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:197
translate french jamie1_42cafbea:

    # gnd "I shut down for a long time. I didn't trust people, didn't make friends easily."
    gnd "Je me suis renfermée pendant très longtemps. Je ne faisais plus confiance aux gens, je ne me faisais plus d’amis facilement."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:199
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_28:

    # voice "voices/jamie_079.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_079.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:200
translate french jamie1_58eb925b:

    # gnd "I mostly just laid in my room and studied and cried."
    gnd "Je passais surtout mon temps allongée dans ma chambre à étudier et à pleurer."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:202
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_29:

    # voice "voices/jamie_080.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_080.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:203
translate french jamie1_f2e0045e:

    # gnd "That's why my dad hates you. He saw what you did to me and he's never forgiven you for it."
    gnd "C’est pour ça que mon père te déteste. Il a vu ce que tu m’as fait et il ne t’a jamais pardonné."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:206
translate french jamie1_10be1c3b:

    # pc "I'm so sorry. I was a stupid kid, but that's no excuse."
    pc "Je suis vraiment désolée. J’étais une gamine stupide, mais ce n’est pas une excuse."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:207
translate french jamie1_bcb802d4:

    # pc "I should have never treated you like that."
    pc "Je n’aurais jamais dû te traiter comme ça."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:209
translate french jamie1_76abefbc:

    # pc "I'm not going to apologize for stuff I did when I was 13 years old. I was a stupid kid. All kids are stupid kids."
    pc "Je ne vais pas m’excuser pour des choses que j’ai faites quand j’avais 13 ans. J’étais une gamine stupide. Tous les enfants sont des gamins stupides."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:212
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_30:

    # voice "voices/jamie_081.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_081.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:213
translate french jamie1_326ba1f0:

    # gnd "You're STILL a stupid kid! I'm done here! This was a mistake! We're not friends, don't talk to me anymore!"
    gnd "Tu es TOUJOURS une gamine stupide ! J’en ai fini ici ! C’était une erreur ! On n’est pas amies, ne m’adresse plus la parole !"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:214
translate french jamie1_6ca9d573:

    # "With that, she stands up and walks out of the café."
    "Sur ces mots, elle se lève et sort du café."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:215
translate french jamie1_01c3f816:

    # "Others avert their gaze from me, trying to pretend that they hadn't heard what just happened."
    "Les autres détournent le regard, essayant de faire comme s’ils n’avaient rien entendu."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:216
translate french jamie1_f5d0b218:

    # "This had not gone anything like what I had wanted. I'm not sure if my relationship with Jamie is even salvageable now."
    "Ça ne s’est pas du tout passé comme je l’avais voulu. Je ne sais même pas si ma relation avec Jamie est encore sauvable maintenant."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:217
translate french jamie1_a686ffdc:

    # "I finish up my coffee, thinking about the mistakes I'd made, then I head back out to the car and go to school."
    "Je finis mon café en repensant aux erreurs que j’ai commises, puis je retourne à la voiture et je pars à l’école."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:223
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_31:

    # voice "voices/jamie_082.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_082.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:224
translate french jamie1_4d43b439:

    # gnd "You have no idea how long I've dreamed about hearing you say that."
    gnd "Tu n’as pas idée depuis combien de temps je rêvais de t’entendre dire ça."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:226
translate french jamie1_b94d1a33:

    # "She takes a deep breath, then reaches across the table and puts her hands on top of mine."
    "Elle prend une grande inspiration, puis tend la main par-dessus la table et pose ses mains sur les miennes."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:229
translate french jamie1_d41d8cd9_32:

    # voice "voices/jamie_083.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_083.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:230
translate french jamie1_fa010ee6:

    # gnd "I forgive you."
    gnd "Je te pardonne."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:231
translate french jamie1_521ec7fb:

    # pc "Thank you. I want to be friends again. Can we start over?"
    pc "Merci. Je veux qu’on soit à nouveau amis. On peut repartir à zéro ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:233
translate french jamie1_07ca4578:

    # gnd "I don't think there's such a thing as starting over, but we can start working on repairing the damage."
    gnd "Je ne pense pas qu’on puisse vraiment repartir à zéro, mais on peut commencer à réparer les dégâts."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:235
translate french jamie1_88df1b89:

    # gnd "This helped a lot."
    gnd "Ça m’a beaucoup aidée."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:236
translate french jamie1_ab6c009b:

    # pc "I'm glad. We should do it again."
    pc "J’en suis ravie. On devrait recommencer."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:237
translate french jamie1_241ea26c:

    # gnd "Definitely. With hopefully less crying."
    gnd "Absolument. Avec, espérons-le, moins de larmes."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:238
translate french jamie1_c8d9b24c:

    # "We finish up our coffees and walk out to the cars together."
    "Nous finissons nos cafés et sortons ensemble vers nos voitures."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:241
translate french jamie1_1b15168b:

    # gnd "Text me sometime, we can go get coffee again or something."
    gnd "Envoie-moi un texto un de ces jours, on pourra aller prendre un café ensemble ou autre chose."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:242
translate french jamie1_9b5f710f:

    # pc "I will, I promise."
    pc "Je le ferai, c’est promis."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:244
translate french jamie1_d311130c:

    # gnd "Thanks for this."
    gnd "Merci pour tout ça."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:245
translate french jamie1_ca03cbd8:

    # pc "No, I should be thanking you for giving me another chance."
    pc "Non, c’est moi qui devrais te remercier de m’avoir donné une autre chance."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:246
translate french jamie1_861e750f:

    # pc "I'm not going to hurt you again, I promise. I'm not the same person I was then."
    pc "Je ne te ferai plus de mal, je te le promets. Je ne suis plus la même personne qu’à l’époque."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:247
translate french jamie1_18b10010:

    # gnd "I know. I can tell."
    gnd "Je sais. Ça se voit."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:249
translate french jamie1_1c4e0503:

    # gnd "I'll see you later."
    gnd "À plus tard."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:250
translate french jamie1_d22c868b:

    # "She gets into her car and drives away, back towards her house."
    "Elle monte dans sa voiture et repart, en direction de chez elle."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:252
translate french jamie1_3aaaf55b:

    # "The coffee date hadn't gone anything like I expected it too, but I am still happy with the outcome."
    "Ce rendez-vous autour d’un café ne s’est pas du tout passé comme je l’avais prévu, mais je suis quand même content du résultat."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:253
translate french jamie1_d14d202f:

    # "Now that everything is out in the open, It feels like I have a real connection with Jamie."
    "Maintenant que tout est au grand jour, j’ai l’impression d’avoir un vrai lien avec Jamie."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:254
translate french jamie1_1cc92515:

    # "I want to treat her right and earn her forgiveness."
    "Je veux la traiter comme il faut et mériter son pardon."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:255
translate french jamie1_26a71157:

    # "If anything else comes after that, great, but I don't expect it. Not after the way I had treated her."
    "Si quelque chose d'autre en découle, tant mieux, mais je ne m'y attends pas. Pas après la façon dont je l'ai traitée."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:256
translate french jamie1_86fdd457:

    # "I get into the car and drive away."
    "Je monte dans la voiture et je pars."

